  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Combine the <strong>ground almonds</strong>, <strong>panko&nbsp;breadcrumbs</strong> and <strong>smoked paprika</strong> in a bowl with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>\r\n<p>Spread half of this <strong>breadcrumb</strong> <strong>mixture</strong> evenly on a large plate</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into bite-size pieces</p>\r\n<p>Add them to a pot of <strong>salted boiled water</strong> and cook over a high heat for 10 min or until&nbsp;almost fork-tender</p>\r\n<p>Trim and cut the <strong>runner beans</strong> into thin strips lengthways, then chop them into small pieces</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, spread the <strong>diced chicken</strong> out onto the <strong>breadcrumb mixture</strong> plate</p>\r\n<p>Top with the other half of the <strong>breadcrumb mixture</strong> and press the chicken firmly into the mixture to coat each piece evenly</p>\r\n<p>Tip: work in batches if your plate is too crowded</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 4 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[8 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>vegetable&nbsp;oil</strong> to a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a matching lid over a medium-high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once&nbsp;hot, add the breadcrumbed chicken in a single layer&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Cover&nbsp;with a lid and cook for 8 min, turning once halfway through or until golden and cooked through - these are your <strong>chicken nuggets&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>honey</strong>, <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong> and <strong>mayonnaise</strong> - this is your <strong>honey mustard dipping sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are almost fork-tender, add the<strong>&nbsp;chopped runner beans</strong> to the pot, cover and cook for a further 3-4 min or until tender</p>\r\n<p>Once done, drain and transfer the <strong>runner beans</strong> to the chicken pan, push the nuggets to the side to keep warm until serving and return the cooked <strong>potatoes</strong> to the pot ready for mashing&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add a large knob of<strong> butter</strong> and a splash of <strong>milk</strong> to the <strong>potatoes</strong> and season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong></p>\r\n<p>Mash thoroughly until the potatoes are smooth</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/559_step-7-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
